# No Modify Existing Policy

Never delete or modify existing resources in Git, Jira, or Azure.

## Scope

- **Git**: No force push, branch deletion, or modification of existing commits on remote.
- **Jira**: No delete or update of existing issues, comments, worklogs, attachments (see no-jira-write for details).
- **Azure**: No create, update, or delete of Azure resources (see azure-read-only for details).

## Exception

Resources created by the agent/workflow during the current session may be modified or deleted (e.g. a branch or PR created by the workflow, a Jira ticket created by the workflow).
